## 🌱 Farmer-Centered Tools

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i></span> Mobile Services
- **Price Alerts** — Real-time updates that learn from market behavior and farmer preferences.
- **Weather Forecasts** — Hyperlocal predictions that adapt to shifting climate patterns and planting cycles.
- **Crop Diagnosis** — AI models that improve with each image submitted, learning from local disease variants.

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></span> Farm Records & Finance
- **Productivity Logs** — Personalized dashboards that adapt to each farmer’s cropping history and input use.
- **Microfinance Access** — Credit scoring models that evolve based on repayment behavior and group dynamics.
- **Community Sharing** — Peer networks that surface relevant tips based on location, crop, and season.

---

## 🧠  Market Intelligence

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></span> Group Intelligence
- **Credit Scoring** — Adaptive models that incorporate behavioral nudges and repayment patterns.
- **Yield Forecasting** — Group-level predictions that refine with each harvest and input cycle.
- **SMS Nudges** — Messaging that evolves based on response rates and seasonal timing.

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i></span> Research & Trials
- **AI Training** — Models that continuously learn from farmer-submitted data and extension feedback.
- **Knowledge Digitization** — NLP systems that refine indigenous knowledge classification over time.
- **Demand Mapping** — Urban consumption trends that adjust based on retail feedback and price shifts.
- **Harvest Forecasting** — Models that improve with each season’s actual harvest data.

---

## 🗺️ Landscape Intelligence

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i></span> Land & Climate Mapping
- **Soil Health Zones** — Maps that refine nutrient profiles as new drone and satellite data is collected.
- **Flood & Drought Risk** — Predictive layers that adjust based on rainfall anomalies and farmer-reported impacts.
- **Crop Suitability Models** — Adaptive algorithms that learn from trial outcomes and yield data.

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></span> Market Linkage & Logistics
- **Smart Routing** — Transport plans that learn from delays, spoilage rates, and road conditions.
- **Adaptive Trials** — Experimental designs that evolve based on zone-specific performance and farmer input.

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-fish"></i></span> Livestock & Aquaculture
- **Disease Detection** — AI that improves with local image/audio samples and vet feedback.
- **IoT Monitoring** — Sensor systems that adjust thresholds based on historical water and growth data.
